short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A script to automatically fill up your Timesheet for you

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: RedMine Timesheet Filler is a convenient script designed to streamline and automate the process of filling up your timesheet in RedMine, a popular project management platform. With this script, you can save valuable time and effort by eliminating the need for manual data entry.
